{"tid":2498230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有香港台唔聽仲聽個死咗既港台係咩玩法？","createTime":"2021-04-21T04:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T04:36:46.000Z","uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"76e99964a9ab3649793bdfcc477660a0a5bed1d1","tid":2498230,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:36:14.000Z","msg":"由真正愛香港精神既鄭敬基攪咗個台，裝個app就聽得<br />\naccount都唔使申請<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongerstation.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongerstation.com%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=bc880523\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongerstation.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n每個鐘都有香港新聞聽，唔使打開電視電台都想打爆部電視同埋收音機<br />\n雖然仍然係初步階段，主打民主人士訪問，以及移民加拿大資訊<br />\n<br />\n但你可以開個app，都仲可以keep住全日有聲<br />\n仲有如果你淨用app聽，<br />\n基本上斷咗線或者offline, 再重新連線<br />\n係會接住你之前聽緊既節目<br />\n<br />\n佢會keep住有野聽<br />\n真係同你聽一般電台無分別<br />\n<br />\n又唔似聽住d 政治kol咁會令自己有道德壓力<br />\n仲有個business model好好，可課金又有廣告<br />\nd廣告仲smooth過商台<br />\n<br />\n不論聽眾燒時間，或者商家落廣告<br />\n香港台都係好選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望可以愈做愈大，愈來愈多野聽"},{"pid":"b8326d0d7914638f5dd631d07eb7fa54137f4eb6","tid":2498230,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:36:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}